<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l15">von vvircʒburg 
<add><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l14">von vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> cʒu haben vnd cʒu nemen maint / 
