<add><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l19">des vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>künicli<ex>chen</ex></expan> etc </ab></add> / Vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Als daʒ vns <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l21">
<del rend="strikethrough">geʒielt hat </del> als vvir auch <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> nehſt ~ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen <expan>heıdelb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l23">cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> geſant haben / den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gnad </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l22"><expan>kunigl<ex>iche</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>hochwir<ex>dikeit</ex></expan> <expan>hinvvid<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l24"> geʒielt 
<del rend="strikethrough">hat </del> hat 
