<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1571058628198_750"><expan>gnedıglıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hochwir<ex>dikeit</ex></expan> <expan>vertige<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>kuniglich<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1571058694476_766">brief <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / das wir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l34">vnd dıe vnſern </ab></add> deſſelben cʒolls <expan>v̈berhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_30_r2l35">vnd damit <expan>umbeſw<ex>er</ex>t</expan> </ab></add> werden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1571058733098_778">Als wir des etc 
<del rend="strikethrough">das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etc <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_r2l40">Auch <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rats <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> geſchıckt etc </ab></del>
